No. 1/34/1/2008-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
y00
New Delhi, the 3rd March, 2009
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 3rd March,
2009 :-
Shri Oscar Fernandes relinquished the charge of the office of
the Minister of State (Independent Charge) of the Ministry of
Labour and Employment; and
i)
Shri G.K.Vasan, Minister of State (Independent Charge) of the
Ministry of Statistics & Programme Implementation assumed
the charge of the office of the Minister of State (Independent
Charge) of the Ministry of Labour and Employment in addition
to the charge of the office of the Minister of State (Independent
Charge) of the Ministry of Statistics & Programme
Implementation held by him.
ii)
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and Members of
the Planning Commission.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Copy forwarded for information to:-
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
(K.L. Sharma)
Director (Cabinet)
Copy also forwarded for information to :-
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
(K.L. Sharma)
Director (Cabinet)
